\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Because as we said\'85a storm is coming. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But the storm isn\'92t the issue\'85it\'92s whether you\'92re ready for the storm.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I mean come on\'85I love storms in real life\'85I watch them\'85I\'92ll pull up a chair and from the safety of my house I\'92ll just watch\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But it\'92s because I\'92m ready for it\'85storms don\'92t scare me\'85because I\'92m prepared.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What will determine whether this is a good year or a bad year is not what happens to you\'85that is a passive way of looking at life and you are NOT simply what has happened to you.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What if this year you could PREHab your life? \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What if instead of hoping bad things wouldn\'92t happen\'85knowing they will\'85what if you are prepared for them.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What if you were intentional about what life will throw at you so when, and it is only a matter of when it happens, you\'92re ready.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We\'92re going to spend the next several weeks talking about the critical areas of your life where you can prepare in advance for a storm that will eventually happen and in doing so are ready to handle the challenge. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
